00:42:27,886 --> 00:42:29,286
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena itulah, besok, aku akan ke Seoul.</font>

683
00:42:33,316 --> 00:42:34,386
<font color=#FFFF00>Bong Hee.</font>

684
00:42:34,537 --> 00:42:41,545
<font color=#FFFF00>{\an8} <i>Wajahmu yang terngiang-ngiang
